column5: Received a report that the office manager is at work at Nakina Air Service. GOOD sign. This means ice is about all off lakes at Nakina and then North.
Anyone going into Beteau in June? WW
It's been a really hot May, I would be surprised if there was much ice left anywhere.
is eddie north still outfitting beteau??
Nope, he is down east doing his thing. Chris Lewis is the new owner.WW
